== Introduction ==

{DRAGORA} is a complete and reliable distribution of the
[GNU/Linux {LINUX_GNU}] operating system that is **entirely**
[free software {FREE_SOFTWARE}].  {DRAGORA} is founded on the concepts
of simplicity and elegance, it can be run for almost any purpose
(desktop, workstation, server, development, etc.).  The intended audience
is people interested in learning more about the technical aspects of a
friendly GNU/Linux distribution.  Also people looking to use the purest
ethical software for daily use.

