=== Bug Reports ===

For general discussion of bugs in Dragora the mailing list
dragora-users@nongnu.org is the most appropriate forum.  Please send
messages as plain text, do not send messages encoded as HTML nor encoded
as base64 MIME nor included as multiple formats.  Please include a
descriptive subject line.  If all of the subject are "bug in dragora" it
is impossible to differentiate them.

=== Translating Dragora ===

Translations of the website and documentation of Dragora are welcome.
Note: we are trying to improve the information in both, website and
documentation before accepting translations.

